{"id":143398,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/图辑：英国推迟核电站计划/","date":"2011-04-06T20:00:28Z","modified":"2011-04-06T20:00:28Z","title":"图辑：英国推迟核电站计划","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143549_sellafield_nuclear_plant_926x521_getty.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国核电站\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143549_sellafield_nuclear_plant_926x521_getty.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>受日本核事故影响，英国将核电站新建计划推迟三个月。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143925_nuclear_reactor_926x521_getty.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"反应堆\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143925_nuclear_reactor_926x521_getty.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>英国政府推迟两座新核电站的兴建计划，好让相关人员从日本福岛核事故中学习经验和记取教训。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144153_nuclear_power_station_926x521_getty.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"核电站\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144153_nuclear_power_station_926x521_getty.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>卫生和安全执行委员会（Health and Safety Executive, HSE）以及环境署（Environment Agency, EA）负责评估新建核电站反应堆的安全。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144430_cow_926x521_getty.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"母牛\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144430_cow_926x521_getty.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>这两个安全评估机构表示，不会按照预定计划在6月公布评估结果。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144637_pylons_926x521_getty.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"电塔\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406144637_pylons_926x521_getty.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>虽然如此，法国EDF能源公司表示，在英国新建核电站的计划不会改变。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143142_cnd_nuclear_protest_926x521_afp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"反核活动\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/04/06/110406143142_cnd_nuclear_protest_926x521_afp.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>此前，反核活动人士在唐宁街对面举行示威集会，要求政府放弃新建两座核电站的计划。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ChbRfYOXWxCCFK1KoNTjJoe2ecE/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ChbRfYOXWxCCFK1KoNTjJoe2ecE/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ChbRfYOXWxCCFK1KoNTjJoe2ecE/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ChbRfYOXWxCCFK1KoNTjJoe2ecE/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/-Z9ExV9gHsU\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):ziyouwangluo2011ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15660]}